text:
This is a Lego stop motion video I made 4 years ago for a music play purpose,
the idea was using lego figures to build some spaceship and let it fly, in that
time I was just starting to learn stop motion with special effects, it was a
great memory, this video took me around 1 month of production and nearly 2500
pictures.

 這部是我4年前剛開始學習定格動畫加上電影特效的影片, 那時是幫五月天拍演唱會MV所用的影片片段, 底是一樣的, 只不過我這部份又另外再自己處理背景特效跟片段,
算是我早期的回憶之一, 這次會PO上來是跟另一個介紹影片一起上傳推廣.

 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uIDR_3x35As
